;\">寫比支那人睇，唔用殘體用乜？</span>"},{"pid":"21254821a1b0562f770a03054400f88b249688ad","tid":709713,"uid":129039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8335ce17081120024d03fc8bf9756ae831dcf9c6","tid":709713,"uid":42731,"like":8,"dislike":69,"score":-61,"quote":{"pid":"843f081cdede0eca4580f14a92c0c5aaa24b119e","tid":709713,"uid":73473,"like":30,"dislike":4,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T09:11:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>殘體字負皮</blockquote>睇唔明都估到啦，你負皮係咪個腦生草呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>依到係香港呀用乜撚殘體字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n知唔知咩叫曲"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T09:13:42.000Z","msg":"曲乜撚野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T10:05:21.000Z","msg":"直必腸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b79b810788033cdd8b40e6cc530be5f9e7952b52","tid":709713,"uid":187714,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"quote":{"pid":"b762f055019d11620a9410b882d5986533f7b9ea","tid":709713,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T08:46:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10217047361843980&amp;set=a.1587362211724.2090003.1465878348&amp;type=3&amp;theater&amp;ifg=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D10217047361843980%26set%3Da.1587362211724.2090003.1465878348%26type%3D3%26theater%26ifg%3D1&d=f1ak%2FKx76gFv0bJ44sDKYJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=375d8837\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10217047361843980&amp;set=a.1587362211724.2090003.1465878348&amp;type=3&amp;theater&amp;ifg=1</a><br />\n<br />\n本人之前以恳切的态度撰写悔过书向党、国、校交心，结果引蛇出洞，令一众魑魅魍魉，牛鬼蛇神&ldquo;大鸣大放&rdquo;，引来以&rdquo;文汇报&rdquo;为首的走资派出来向无产阶级举行了猖狂的进攻，诬蔑本人悔过书内容「冷嘲热讽」，正如毛主席1957年批判&rdquo;文汇报&rdquo;的伟大言论所说，这种资产阶级方向应当批判，不可令党令国走邪路歪路。<br />\n<br />\n今日，大湾区港浸大校委干部正式批准本人如期毕业，可见港浸大校方&rdquo;任凭风浪起，稳坐钓鱼船&rdquo;的坚定信念，了解本人